		   		<div class="comment-entry">

				<p>This is a very helpful post &#8211; thank you!</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been thinking a lot about this lately, and I&#8217;ve noticed how different little ideas will start to click together. Sometimes it&#8217;ll take months, but I&#8217;ll suddenly have a connection between A and B. It&#8217;s pretty neat. Just another good reason why you should write down anything that pops into your head!</p>

				
